Aguero gets ready to take his spot-kick as Mascherano gestures to his keeper Marc-Andre ter Stegen

Ter Stegen guesses correctly to save Aguero's effort and deny City a lifeline in the 78th minute  

Mascherano rushes to congratulate Ter Stegen following his penalty save late on at the Nou Camp 

Ter Stegen admitted that Mascherano advised him but he decided to make up his own mind in the end 

Lo and behold, Aguero fired his penalty effort in the same direction with Ter Stegen taking Mascherano's advice and diving the same way.

Mascherano admitted trying to advise his keeper on which way to dive for Aguero's penalty. 'I know from international duty how he takes spot-kicks,' said the midfielder after the game. 

Ter Stegen admitted being advised by both Mascherano and Rafinha but in the end made his own mind up.  

Manchester City were eliminated at the last 16 stage after failing to overturn their first-leg deficit

